caption: Competent, friendly and smiling team. Much better maintained cemetery.  Small suggestion: On the Bel Air entrance side, could we install a seat on level 18, square 11, in front of the old graves for example. There is one on the other side, in square 12.  With my thanks.
A priori during my passage outside I noticed no parking for vehicles or bicycles but there is a shuttle bus passage
The staff very welcoming and always available. In addition, they always provide you with very good information with great kindness. Keep it up, you guys are great :)

Easy to access with an entrance on each side. The cemetery is divided in two and separated by a street. If you know the part in which the tomb you are looking for is located then there is not much distance to go.
Staff always attentive. Very beautiful cemetery. Thanks to the municipality for the latest work carried out.
Very pleasant cemetery. Very nice embellishment following the latest work. And thank you to the caretaker for her welcome and her kindness.
Nice cemetery, long time since I came. Thanks to the lady for directing me to the grave I was looking for. Thanks to her!
How sad this cemetery. There are herbs in every path. A lack of maintenance which is becoming unacceptable.
Very warm welcome, thank you to the caretaker for her sympathy and dedication!
very beautiful cemetery with a tribute (stele) to the Indochinese fighters.
Quite calm, problem there is not enough atmosphere
Very large place of contemplation. Well maintained.
